communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Nebraska Public Records Act, I hereby request the following records:

The full police report for Peter Baldwin on November 14, 2023. Also any and all body cam and police car camera footage in full video from time of Peter Baldwin being pulled over till his incarceration, obtaining to the specific traffic stop and incidences follow that initial contact  A request for all available documentation on injury report and pictures and/ or video inquiring that information as well. 
I think you for taking the time to do the due diligence and send these necessary public records to the email listed or if it will not fit on email then some sort of media like CD-ROM or SD card or USB drive. Thank you again the email address is listed below.

Sincerely, Peter Baldwin

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 4 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Peter Baldwin
